    survival,
    survminer,
    gt,
    forestplot,
    IPDfromKM,
    ggplot2,
    stats,
    utils,
    grid
SystemRequirements: GNU make
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
